{
  "stem": "10572.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And after I left school, I was put into an apprenticeship program with a schneidermeister, with a master tailor, who had many, many years ago had books from my father and was very, very proud that Willy Schurmann came to him to ask him to take his son under his wings.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was at that time 17.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was an amazing transition for me coming from this kind of snobbish school and going to be for-- at 7 o'clock every morning sit on the table with crossed legs and be taught by this man whose German was grammatically not quite correct.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was an uneducated man, at least I thought by my standards.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But after a while he taught me that my [LATIN], and the fact that I knew how to say [LATIN] in Latin didn't mean a damn thing to him.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that I was really a dummkopf, that I was a stupid boy who couldn't be taught as easily as he thought he could teach me.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But he finally convinced me that I set my mind to it and I spent two years with him.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that was-- the-- the apprentice system was, in the retrospect today, I feel a very, very wise system.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it taught us not only to learn the technique of a craft, but also become aware of the social problems connected with it.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I would live in this magnificent home, and every morning I would go into this poor neighborhood and sit on the table together with Schneidermeister Hemholdt and learned how-- the very basic things, how to make a pair-- pair of trousers.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it took me many, many months before I even was half productive.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he put lots of his own effort into it.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
